                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8394" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">TM-0025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1486 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">美好生活服务商：开元旅业集团“酒+景”差异化战略进阶之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">From Lodging to Destination: The Differentiation Strategy of New Century Tourism Group</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">彭雪蓉，王红，梁燕浩，王节祥（通讯作者）</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">开元旅业集团</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">20 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">差异化战略；景区化；社区化；数字化；开元旅业集团</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Differentiation; Scenic-ification; Community-ification; Digitalization; New Century Tourism Group</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">差异化战略是企业产品、服务、形象等有别于竞争对手而带来顾客感知价值提升以获得竞争优势的战略。本案例描述了中国最大的民营高端酒店集团——开元旅业集团近年来以“美好生活服务商”为战略定位，以“酒+景”为转型突破口，综合运用“减加乘”的差异化思路，探索“试水→进阶→迭代→沉淀→复制”的业态创新模式，从旅游产业链的“住宿配套”转变为“旅游吸引物和目的地”，进而实现高绩效增长的过程。通过本案例的学习，学员可以更好地理解差异化战略的内涵、形式、动因，以及差异化实施的必要条件、成功关键要素和风险规避策略，并利用“加减乘”思路进行差异化思考。此外，本案例还有助于学员了解新时期酒店产业发展的新趋势（景区化、社区化、数字化和绿色化），辨别“酒+景”和“景+酒”两种商业模式的差异。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The differentiation strategy is a key competitive approach aimed at setting products, services, and brand image apart from those of competitors to increase perceived customer value. This case study illustrates how New Century Tourism Group, the largest private upscale hotel chain in China, has embraced the strategic positioning of being a &quot;Wonderful Life Service Provider&quot; to steer its business model transformation and attain impressive financial performance. New Century Tourism Group has shifted its strategic focus from being merely an &quot;accommodation support&quot; business in the tourism industry chain to becoming a &quot;Wonderful Life Service Provider&quot;, with &quot;Hotels + Scenic Sports&quot; as a key breakthrough for transformation. The company has pursued a business innovation model of &quot;trial, advance, iteration, precipitation, and replication&quot; by implementing a differentiation strategy that emphasizes &quot;subtraction, addition, and multiplication&quot;. This approach has enabled the company to strategically position itself to concentrate on &quot;tourism attraction and destination&quot;. By examining this case study, students can gain an in-depth comprehension of the meaning, forms, and drivers of differentiation strategy, as well as the fundamental requirements, key success factors, and risk mitigation measures entailed in its implementation. The case study encourages students to think creatively, utilizing the &quot;addition, subtraction, and multiplication&quot; approach to differentiation. Additionally, it highlights the emerging trends in the hotel industry, such as scenic-ification; community-ification, digitalization, and green, and clarifies the differences between the two business models of &quot;Hotels + Scenic Sports&quot; and &quot;Scenic Sports + Hotels &quot;.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《酒店战略管理》 </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">资源基础观；竞争战略与竞争优势；VRIO模型</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-06</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
